            <title>[HBASE-8828] Port HBASE-4460 to Thrift 2</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8828</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4460&quot; title=&quot;Support running an embedded ThriftServer within a RegionServer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4460&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4460&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; adds the ability to start an embedded Thrift server inside a RegionServer. Port it to Thrift 2, or make it optional which it starts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
